{"id": "2298", "post": "<div class=\"post-2298 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial\" id=\"post-2298\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/running-out-of-time-and-i-am-taking-a-break/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Running out of time\u2026 and I am taking a break</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> December 11, 2011 @ 1:00 pm, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p>Just a quick note on what will be happening over the next couple of days.</p><ul><li><b>I am running out of time</b>. Apology to all the providers who have emailed me their Christmas specials (and in some cases, <em>just</em> repeats of their previous offers), and sorry I won\u2019t be able to fulfil all your requests. I haven\u2019t even really started on my \u201cDead Pool November 2011\u201d post yet (although there were some discussions on last month\u2019s dead pool list <a href=\"http://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/751/dead-pool-november-2011-discussion#Item_14\">at LowEndTalk.com</a>).</li><li><b>I am also taking a break</b>, and will take my family on a road trip for a few days. 350km drive tomorrow and there are still lots to be packed. There won\u2019t be new blog posts here either, but feel free to continue the discussion at the <a href=\"http://www.lowendtalk.com/\">LowEndTalk site</a>.</li></ul><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=